    - "inspect.getsource.__qualname__ == 'getsource' (len 9) — getsource is defined at module scope in Lib/inspect.py. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "inspect.getsource.__module__ == 'inspect'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "inspect.getsource.__code__.co_argcount == 1 — takes one positional argument (object). Verified with Python 3.14.3."
